      <title>以色列与哈马斯达成停火协议后加沙局势如何？</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-17/after-israel-hamas-ceasefire-deal-what-now-for-gaza</link>
      <description><![CDATA[经过15个月的战争，以色列和哈马斯宣布暂停敌对行动。在最好的情况下，为期六周的停火将无限期延长，这将带来一系列新挑战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-17/after-israel-hamas-ceasefire-deal-what-now-for-gaza</guid>
